          "speedKmph": 42,
          "fixFailed": false,
          "position": { "latitude": 41.8781, "longitude": -87.6298 }
        }
      },
      "source": "synthetic",
      "_note": "Synthetic in-bounds fix; bytes built so int32 LE lat/lon*1e-7 = 41.8781,-87.6298, heading 90, speed 42 km/h, batV 4.0. expected.data derived by running reference/upstream-codec.js and remapping to the normalized vocabulary."
    },
    {
      "description": "fPort 1 position, valid fix, not in trip (TTN example input)",
